						<div class="postbody">Folks I want to drive two consoles simultaneously with one controller.<br /><br />The reason being I want to test various clones against the real nes with the same games to test for lag.<br /><br />I have spliced 2 nes extension cables into a y adapter and quickly learned it's not as easy as that.<br /><br />Has a one done this before? Tips?</div>

