					<td>
					

						<div class="postbody">Put two shift registers in the same controller. Connect the output pins to different consoles, and the clock/reset pins to the different consoles, too. I believe there's enough space for it in the controller, adding the 2nd wire shouldn't be too bad either.</div>

					
